cards.desc:
**Prerequisites: **

Network connection.

**Description:**
User navigates to a bottom of Science page and subscribes to "Pangaia" site with invalid data.

**Steps to reproduce:**

1.Go to “https://pangaia.com/ page.

2.Select a Science tab and go to bottom of the page.

2.Fill in email section with "22@22" fake email data.
3.Select a name and type in "!" sign.
4.Click Subscribe button.

**Expected result:
User should not be able to subscribe with invalid and inpropriate data.

**Actual result:**
User is subscribed to "Pangaia" page. "Thanks for subscribing" message is displayed on the screen.
cards.name: User subscribes with fake and inappropriate data.

Prerequisites:

Existing user account. User should be logged in to the page.

Description:
User selects specific round trip fllight for a specific period of time with 1 pasenger and economy class. Afther selecting a specific flight from available flights user proceeds for a booking and payment. By clicking on “Book now“ button “404 Error Page not Found“ error message is displayed. 

Steps to reproduce:

1.Go to “https://phptravels.net/“ page.

2.Select a flight from Istanbul to Sarajevo, from 06.05.2022 to 09.05.2022 with  1 adults and economy class.

2.Select search button.
3.Select first flight in the list of available flights and click on Book now button.

Expected result:
User should proceed to a payement method page.

Actual result:
Error message “ button “404 Error Page not Found“ is displayed.

cards.desc:
When clicking on a button to get us notified when a new order arrives, popup window shows up. But in that window senetences are written in missorder and font is too small.

Steps to reproduce
1. Go to Women page and select specific item.
2. Select a size that is not currently available.
3. Select "Notify me" button and check for a message.

Expected result:
A plain and right message should be displayed.
Actual result:
The font is too small and there is no any punctation. A point is missing between senetences.

**Prerequisites: **

Network connection.

**Description:**
User clicks on a specific link situated in details page of that item, afther that user is navigated to an empty page where no content is available.

**Steps to reproduce:**

1.Go to “https://pangaia.com/ page.

2.Select a Men>Shorts>InStock>JadeGreen specific item. Afther this user is navigated to details page.

2.Click on Details section in details page, select "Find out more" link  and click on it.

**Actual result:**
No information is provided. "This site can’t be reached" error is displayed.

Cards from this board get into the Kanban board (for development) when necessary or when there's room in the schedule. The team negotiates this with the PM / PO so that Technical Debt remains manageable and doesn't become a problem.

listing.name: Jira
listing.description:
Connect Jira and Trello to help all your teams work better together. The Jira Power-up allows you to...

* Link Jira issues to cards, connecting different Workspaces across your organization.
* View important issue information on the detailed card view.
* See if your linked issues are done at glance (from the front of the card)
* Automatically links the Jira issue back to a Trello card so everyone in your team knows how something came to be.
* Quickly jump to your Jira project by creating a link on your board.

### Screenshot

![Back of card Jira section](https://jira-trello-integration.us-east-1.prod.public.atl-paas.net/images/jello-screenshot.png)
listing.overview: Eliminate context switching and ensures every member of your team is always on the same page.
